description: Boat Slip 44ft at Semiahmoo near Blaine Washington. This is a very beautiful, secure, friendly well run and well maintained marina. Wide docks, picnic area, small store with some marine parts, snacks, lunch bar and soft drinks as well as wine and beer. Lots of free parking. All manner of sea birds and eagles populate Drayton Harbor and surrounding areas. Semiahmoo Spit has a black topped walking path with little traffic and right along the beach. Modern clean showers, Wifi and just a few minutes walk to Semiahmoo Resort and Spa. There is a lively community of boaters here, with activities such as Friday night barbeques and music in the summer. Semiahmoo has the cheapest fuel rates of all the local marinas. You also save fuel by being close to the San Juan and Canadian Gulf Islands. If you like fishing, Boundary Bay and Pt Whitehorn are just a few miles away. A short dingy ride gets you to White Rock B.C. with many restaurants and great night life. Semiahmoo is only 8 minutes from I-5 and all this for $45 a month less than Blaine or Squalicum Harbors and hundreds less than Vancouver B.C. We are looking for a long term lease. The slip number is C-16 and is close to the ramp, easy in and out of the slip. Prevailing winds set you off the dock. This is a link to more information about Semiahmoo Marina http://semiahmoomarina.com/our-community/around-the-marina-photo-gallery December Special - sign up before 31 Dec and receive 30% off, until 31 March 2017. PH show contact info
title: 44 Ft Boat Slip For Lease 361.25 a Month
